    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require substantial mechanical work to return to the road. It currently suffers from a failing transmission and significant engine trouble that prevents it from running reliably. The body shows heavy rust, numerous dents, and the interior has seen better days with significant wear and tear. It is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project restorer or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
